Feature: Engorgio (Engorgement Charm)

    Causes objects to swell in size.

    Pronunciation:
        /ɛŋˈɡɔrdʒi.oʊ/ eng-GOR-jee-oh
    Seen/mentioned:
        A "Growth Charm" with the same effect is briefly mentioned. Hagrid is
        suspected of having performed the charm on his pumpkins in Chamber of
        Secrets. Also seen in Goblet of Fire when Barty Crouch Jr,
        impersonating Moody, casts it on a spider to enhance a demonstration of
        the effects of the Cruciatus Curse.
